Even little details--

00:16:05.480 --> 00:16:07.470
IAN NI-LEWIS: I see what
you did there.

00:16:07.470 --> 00:16:08.280
It has legs.

00:16:08.280 --> 00:16:09.130
Nice.

00:16:09.130 --> 00:16:09.610
DAN GALPIN: I know.

00:16:09.610 --> 00:16:10.380
I know.

