bad review, this is one that

00:17:00.600 --> 00:17:01.850
the team finds kind
of borderline.

00:17:04.420 --> 00:17:07.089
And it's this side of goofball
because you can actually tell

00:17:07.089 --> 00:17:07.950
whether they've reviewed it.

00:17:07.950 --> 00:17:10.760
So what usually happens
