things that are outlined and

00:19:46.460 --> 00:19:46.910
some things are not.

00:19:46.910 --> 00:19:49.070
IAN NI-LEWIS: Yeah, the stars
have a little bit

00:19:49.070 --> 00:19:51.370
of a bevel to them.

00:19:51.370 --> 00:19:52.330
It's just really inconsistent.

00:19:52.330 --> 00:19:52.920
DAN GALPIN: I love the
the background.

00:19:52.920 --> 00:19:55.192
