everything take the style of

00:19:55.192 --> 00:19:56.510
the background.

00:19:56.510 --> 00:19:57.470
IAN NI-LEWIS: You're right.

00:19:57.470 --> 00:19:58.970
The background is
kind of cool.

00:19:58.970 --> 00:19:59.570
DAN GALPIN: I love that style.

00:19:59.570 --> 00:20:01.790
I think it also scales
really, really well.

00:20:01.790 --> 00:20:05.310
