The outline wasn't there at all,
and we actually chose an

00:20:28.325 --> 00:20:30.310
art style that was more
consistent with the nice

00:20:30.310 --> 00:20:32.310
gradient fills of
the background.

00:20:32.310 --> 00:20:34.400
I think it would look
a little bit better.

00:20:34.400 --> 00:20:37.700
Don't want to say a lot about
this game, it's just there's a

00:20:37.700 --> 00:20:39.080
lot of polish that
can be done here.

00:20:39.080 --> 00:20:42.830
And I think we did look at it a
long time ago, but my memory

00:20:42.830 --> 00:20:44.580
is such that I don't
even know.

00:20:44.580 --> 00:20:46.320
"Mibo" is kind of interesting.

00:20:46.320 --> 00:20:48.250
The main thing, dude, if you're
going to use AndEngine,

