00:32:05.096 --> 00:32:06.840
DAN GALPIN: Totally.

00:32:06.840 --> 00:32:09.860
Well, I think in general, I want
to see games that take

00:32:09.860 --> 00:32:11.300
advantage of the connectivity.

00:32:11.300 --> 00:32:14.850
Most of these are like 100%
connected devices.

00:32:14.850 --> 00:32:17.590
And I'd love to see RTS games,
and not only to play against

00:32:17.590 --> 00:32:19.990
