experience if clicking
on a Zerg had cost

00:33:00.840 --> 00:33:05.040
me 5/10 of a cent.

00:33:05.040 --> 00:33:05.550
DAN GALPIN: No, that's true.

00:33:05.550 --> 00:33:05.970
That's true.

00:33:05.970 --> 00:33:07.870
IAN NI-LEWIS: And when we're
talking about bandwidth caps

00:33:07.870 --> 00:33:09.160
and stuff like that,
it's really hard--

00:33:09.160 --> 00:33:09.875
DAN GALPIN: Oh, I thought
you were talking

00:33:09.875 --> 00:33:12.290
about in-app purchases.

00:33:12.290 --> 00:33:12.970
IAN NI-LEWIS: Well, that too.

