Try carting around
your desktop.

00:48:34.340 --> 00:48:35.240
DAN GALPIN: Well,
we did that too.

00:48:35.240 --> 00:48:38.130
But I mean, that's why the
Xboxes seemed like, oh, this

00:48:38.130 --> 00:48:40.070
is so easy compared to
carting around--

00:48:40.070 --> 00:48:40.358
IAN NI-LEWIS: Right.

