understand, then they're going

00:59:29.460 --> 00:59:32.300
to see this and they're going to
think, oh, I guess Android

00:59:32.300 --> 00:59:35.400
games are all full of
gigantic pixels.

00:59:35.400 --> 00:59:38.480
And I mean, maybe that was
a reasonable fear.

00:59:38.480 --> 00:59:39.390
Maybe it wasn't.

00:59:39.390 --> 00:59:40.460
DAN GALPIN: But if you
put it in a retro

00:59:40.460 --> 00:59:41.420
